     H            Y.
     F** UEXR40B ********************************************
     F*  EXSUB- UPDATE ANNUAL VOLUME                        *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2021.01.21                       *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR40B'
     F*                    PARM           $MHIN  20
     F*                    PARM           $YSLS   9
     F*                    PARM           $MM     2
     F*  IN: $MHIN  20A  USER PART
     F*      $YSLS   9A  ANNUAL VOLUME
     F*      $MM     2A  MONTH
     F******************************************************
     FMBDWP86 UF  E           K        DISK
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $MHIN  20
     C                     PARM           $YSLS   9
     C                     PARM           $MM     2
     C                     MOVEL$YSLS     @YSLS   90
     C                     MOVEL$MM       @MM     20
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
      *
     C           $MHIN     SETLLMBDWP86
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           $MHIN     READEMBDWP86                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C                     Z-ADD@YSLS     M6YSLS
     C           @YSLS     DIV  @MM       M6MSLS
     C                     UPDATMBDWP861
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
